snippet.textDisplay: It's an honor to be part of CS this year and sharing the platform with the powerhouse of talent, from singers I have been listening to when i was a child and right now being nostalgic just to hear them back, sharing the season with them is on a different level all together to legends like Abida Jee, and the whole line up from Nagma to Attah Ullah Sahab to Hassan Jahangir to Jawad Ahmed, everyone is super amazing. One thing that i am loving the most is I am the first one to represent my Hunza here and loving the fact that CS is focusing so much on diversity and pluralism this year!!! No matter what happen next for me this season will be memorable for me... :)
snippet.textOriginal: It's an honor to be part of CS this year and sharing the platform with the powerhouse of talent, from singers I have been listening to when i was a child and right now being nostalgic just to hear them back, sharing the season with them is on a different level all together to legends like Abida Jee, and the whole line up from Nagma to Attah Ullah Sahab to Hassan Jahangir to Jawad Ahmed, everyone is super amazing. One thing that i am loving the most is I am the first one to represent my Hunza here and loving the fact that CS is focusing so much on diversity and pluralism this year!!!
